1) If you need proper animation of folding propellers, use .dll from 7.4.1 version of Firespitter. Seems like 7.4.2 has a little patch to FSAnimateGeneric which breaks it. Reported already to patch author too.

2) If you want to get rid of crashes like this disable HighlightFX in game options. It happens with other mods (like BDArmory rotating bomb rack). Probalby, not a firespitter bug at all.
